{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"9acce04449","title":"致刘伯承、邓小平电","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"e52b1e1f0e","index":0,"year":1946,"month":9,"day":8,"articleId":"9acce04449"}],"tags":[{"id":"5bd9678625","name":"邓小平","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji22","name":"毛泽东全集第22卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji22.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji22":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"1bf161fd40","type":"paragraph","text":"致刘伯承、邓小平电”","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"9acce04449"},{"id":"fcb4d212cd","type":"paragraph","text":"（1946年9月8日）刘、邓：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"9acce04449"},{"id":"6c02c15c6c","type":"paragraph","text":"七日十三时电悉，甚好甚感。如能纤灭川军三个旅，刘崎此次进攻即可打破","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"9acce04449"},{"id":"10fd102aed","type":"paragraph","text":"军委","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"9acce04449"},{"id":"daa848388e","type":"paragraph","text":"八日七时D这是毛泽东为中共中央军委起草的给置载普豫野战军司令员刘伯承和政治委员邓小平的电报。211946年9月7日13时，刘伯承、邓小平、滕代远、张际春致电军委，电文如下：“第三师（军）两个旅全部已被我牙，并获战车六辆。第四十七师（军）之一个旅亦被我全部消灭，另一个旅在白茅集正被我围死中，估计可迅速解决战斗。另四十一师之一二五旅大部（一个团又两个营）在东明全被我包围，正激战中。”","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"9acce04449"}],"page":{"id":"923979e624","publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"9acce04449","start":140,"end":140}}}},"__N_SSG":true}